      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 15 article: Rhodia bought ChiRex for $510 million, not $510 billion</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A report in the Company News column of Business Day on Tuesday about the purchase of ChiRex, a manufacturer for the pharmaceutical industry, by the French chemical company Rhodia misstated the price. It is $510 million, not $510 billion.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
